events.title: CID Case Updates Meeting Canceled
events.description: A meeting scheduled to provide updates on a CID case, involving the Acting AD, DADs, and an ESU Briefer, was canceled. The email notes a prior room change.

keyFacts: An internal meeting regarding a CID (Criminal Investigative Division) case was canceled on March 27, 2019.
The meeting was to involve high-level personnel: an Acting Assistant Director, Deputy Assistant Directors, and an ESU (Executive Staff Unit?) Briefer.
The email was marked as high importance and referenced a prior room change for the meeting.
